  "narration_text": "Unedited footage is a headache, but with DirectorsCut, you can transform raw clips into polished product showcases in minutes. This agentic CLI tool handles everything: from diagnostic checks to full cloud-based analysis and rendering. The result is pure magic\u2014complete with editable JSON decisions, modular video-only workflows, and AI-generated narration. You can even add TikTok-style synced subtitles or use local voice cloning for total privacy. One set of footage, infinite creative prompts. Experience the future of automated editing with DirectorsCut.",
