  "reasoning": "The edit strictly follows the user's 13-point narrative arc while condensing the footage to a punchy ~80-second product walkthrough. To maintain momentum and fulfill the 'speed up render waits' request, I used jump-cuts between the start and end of various processing tasks. Titles are positioned at the bottom to avoid obscuring the macOS terminal UI. Most available clips were utilized to show the full breadth of the tool's features, transitioning quickly between each capability to create a high-energy demo feel."
